Saki West bụ ọchịchị ime Obodo dị na Oyo Steeti, Naịjirịa
Isi ụlọ ọrụ ya dị n'obodo Saki
Shaki, Naịjirịa dị na njedebe nke steeti Oyo

O nwere ebe obibi nke 2nd Mechanised division nke Nigerian Army, Oke-Ogun Polytechnic (TOPS), Technical College na School of Command.
Shaki, Naịjirịa bụkwa otu n'ime obodo kachasị ukwuu na steeti Oyo.
O nwere mpaghara nke 2,014 km2 na ọnụ ọgụgụ mmadụ 278,002 na ọnụego na afọ 2006.
Koodu post nke mpaghara ahụ bụ 203.
